name: o_god_the_mail_16
description: How organized do I have to be to be considered functioning? It's like life was designed to be tedious, or maybe it just became that way through the gradual accumulation of modern requirements that seem dumb. Did ancient people fret about forgetting things or was it obvious? Did they have things that they lost track of and worried about and little ledgers they needed to keep tabs on because ... o God, the mail.
